  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-119fve5\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"79-ymKSx\"><span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=724865143&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E7%A2%87%E7%9C%9F%E5%97%A3&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">碇真嗣<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>如果是女性那么人物争议会少很多，社会对男性是有更高的要求的，但问题在于并不是所有男性都有能力与意愿去承担更多的义务。如果只是没有意愿还好一点，<span class=\"highlight-wrap other\" data-highlight-id=\"1900057016875069605\" data-highlight-split-type=\"both\" data-highlight-id-extra=\"\">缺乏能力（心理素质，身体素质，性格特征）去承担“男性义务”那就糟糕了—</span>我们可以设想一下，一个男性也有可能胆小怯懦，见到虫子就吓得发抖，也有可能身体素质极差，女生的800米都达不到要求，还有可能抗压能力差，稍微一刺激就哭起来。</p><p data-pid=\"AeTbpEM5\"><span class=\"highlight-wrap other\" data-highlight-id=\"1900974999944290525\" data-highlight-split-type=\"both\" data-highlight-id-extra=\"\">这群人在社会上是严重失声的，可能他们自己也不敢发声，也没什么人替他们发声。他们交不到什么朋友，精神状态也很堪忧，还很容易遭受各种欺凌，不少人后来还变成了mtf—这也在一定程度上解释了为何mtf圈子充满了戾气，阴郁与自恨倾向…</span></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3efef760920d34641663769a6f9b9a74_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"800\" data-rawheight=\"824\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-74d407cfecdd2fc077ceff5a426288d6\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-a7b1b6cfaaa320e37ba18c8ca37a2e16_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"800\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-3efef760920d34641663769a6f9b9a74_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='800' height='824'></svg>\" data-rawwidth=\"800\" data-rawheight=\"824\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-74d407cfecdd2fc077ceff5a426288d6\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-a7b1b6cfaaa320e37ba18c8ca37a2e16_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"800\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-3efef760920d34641663769a6f9b9a74_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3efef760920d34641663769a6f9b9a74_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"hbuMCxov\"><span class=\"highlight-wrap other\" data-highlight-id=\"1900126636650787013\" data-highlight-split-type=\"head\" data-highlight-id-extra=\"\">当然，你要是像</span><span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=724865143&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%B3%A2%E4%BC%8F%E5%A8%83&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"highlight-wrap other\" data-highlight-id=\"1900126636650787013\" data-highlight-split-type=\"none\" data-highlight-id-extra=\"\">波伏娃</span><svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span><span class=\"highlight-wrap other\" data-highlight-id=\"1900126636650787013\" data-highlight-split-type=\"tail\" data-highlight-id-extra=\"\">一样认为社会对男性有更高的要求是一件好事，而女性的困境就在于…就当我没说。</span></p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
